Fingerprinting Strategy:

| Component    | Data Collected                 | Privacy Protection        |
| ------------ | ------------------------------ | ------------------------- |
| **CPU**      | Core count, platform           | No model/serial           |
| **Memory**   | Rounded to 2GB                 | No exact bytes            |
| **Screen**   | Resolution, ratio, color depth | No pixel-perfect tracking |
| **Graphics** | GPU category only              | No specific model names   |
| **Locale**   | Timezone, primary language     | No geolocation            |
| **Features** | WebGL, WASM support            | No capability enumeration |

Security Features:

Fuzzy Matching: 70% similarity threshold allows minor hardware changes
Tamper Detection: Identifies spoofing attempts (resolution/GPU changes)
Component Export: Selective export for license storage
Cache Management: 24-hour cache with stability scoring